description: Show the history for one or more labels on the Container App.

commands.name: az containerapp label-history list
commands.summary: List the history for all labels on the Container App.
examples: az containerapp label-history list -n my-containerapp -g MyResourceGroup

commands.name: az containerapp label-history show
commands.summary: Show the history for a specific label on the Container App.
examples: az containerapp label-history show -n my-containerapp -g MyResourceGroup --label LabelName
